HEADWORD: Vespillo
<hw>Ves*pil"lo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Vespilloes</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L.]</ety> <fld>(Rom.
